trans-unit.source: The type of an element in the controlled sequence.
trans-unit.target: 受控制序列中項目的類型。

trans-unit.source: Supports simple iteration over any STL/CLR object that implements the <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.IVector`1" /> interface.
trans-unit.target: 支援在任何實作 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.IVector`1" /> 介面的 STL/CLR 物件上進行簡單的反覆運算。

trans-unit.source: The container over which to iterate.
The offset of the current first element in the container.
trans-unit.target: 容器中目前第一個項目的位移。

trans-unit.source: Allocates and initializes a new <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.VectorEnumerator`1" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 配置並初始化新的 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.VectorEnumerator`1" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the current element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定集合中目前的項目。

trans-unit.source: The current element in the collection.
Frees, releases, or resets unmanaged resources that are used by the <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.VectorEnumerator`1" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 釋出、釋放或重設 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.VectorEnumerator`1" /> 物件所使用的 Unmanaged 資源。

trans-unit.source: Frees, releases, or resets unmanaged resources that are used by the <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.VectorEnumerator`1" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 釋出、釋放或重設 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.VectorEnumerator`1" /> 物件所使用的 Unmanaged 資源。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> to dispose of managed objects; <see langword="false" /> to dispose of unmanaged objects.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> 以處置 Managed 物件；<see langword="false" /> 以處置 Unmanaged 物件。

trans-unit.source: Frees, releases, or resets unmanaged resources that are used by the <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.VectorEnumerator`1" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 釋出、釋放或重設 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualC.StlClr.VectorEnumerator`1" /> 物件所使用的 Unmanaged 資源。

trans-unit.source: Advances the enumerator to the next element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 將列舉值設為集合中的下一個項目。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the enumerator was successfully advanced to the next element; <see langword="false" /> if the enumerator has passed the end of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 如果列舉值成功前移至下一個項目，則為 <see langword="true" />；如果列舉值超過集合的結尾，則為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Sets the enumerator to its initial position, which is before the first element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 設定列舉值至它的初始位置，這是在集合中第一個項目之前。
